    <p>The Great Brony Bake-Off. Whose Line is it Everypony&#8230; karaoke. These are just some of the weird and wonderful things that have graced out meet schedules over the last four years of meets. </p>
    <p>Unfortunately over time we&#8217;ve variously phased them out due to logistical issues, waning interest, or just being too expensive to do regularly and they&#8217;ve not been replaced with anything new. This kinda sucks, and while we want to continue doing interesting and unique things in the meet-space it&#8217;s tough to come up with fresh ideas within these constraints. </p>
    <p>As such, we&#8217;re opening up the floor. If you have a fresh, fun, interesting (and cheap) idea that you think we could do, drop an email to <a href="mailto:kim@severnbronies.co.uk">kim@severnbronies.co.uk</a> and we&#8217;ll consider it for inclusion in the future! </p>
    <p>With that out the way, here&#8217;s our meet. </p>
